      "raw": "{\"prompt\": \"Create a 3×3 grid poster for Xiaohongshu (小红书) female wellness lifestyle content.\\n\\nStyle/medium: needs a clean, premium, cohesive aesthetic with soft治愈 (healing) vibes — exact stylistic execution is yours\\nComposition: must be a 3×3 grid layout (3 columns × 3 rows), with clear boundaries between each cell for easy cropping into 9 individual posts; each cell must be centered and complete, no text near grid lines\\nSubject: must include all 9 cells with specific content:\\n  Cell 1 (cover): main title \\\"让你倒头就睡的8个 tips\\\", subtitle \\\"失眠党、熬夜党一定要收藏\\\", visual elements: soft bed, moon, pillow, eye mask\\n  Cell 2: title \\\"1. 睡前1小时别玩手机\\\", body \\\"蓝光会让大脑更清醒，越刷越睡不着。\\\", elements: phone, moon, sleepy expression illustration\\n  Cell 3: title \\\"2. 睡前把灯光调暗\\\", body \\\"暖光环境能帮助身体进入\\\"准备睡觉\\\"的状态。\\\", elements: bedside lamp, warm yellow light, curtains\\n  Cell 4: title \\\"3. 房间温度别太高\\\", body \\\"稍微凉一点，更容易快速入睡。\\\", elements: AC, thermometer, blanket\\n  Cell 5: title \\\"4. 晚上别喝浓茶咖啡\\\", body \\\"咖啡因会延迟困意，让你躺很久还睡不着。\\\", elements: coffee cup, tea cup, prohibition symbol\\n  Cell 6: title \\\"5. 睡前洗个热水澡\\\", body \\\"能让身体放松下来，入睡速度更快。\\\", elements: bathroom steam, towel, hot water\\n  Cell 7: title \\\"6. 脑子停不下来就写下来\\\", body \\\"把烦心事和待办清单写下，大脑会更容易放松。\\\", elements: notebook, pen, small desk lamp\\n  Cell 8: title \\\"7. 固定上床时间\\\", body \\\"每天差不多时间睡，生物钟会越来越稳定。\\\", elements: clock, moon, bed\\n  Cell 9: title \\\"8. 试试深呼吸放松法\\\", body \\\"吸气4秒，停4秒，呼气6秒，慢慢就有困意了。\\\", footer \\\"收藏这组，今晚试试看\\\", elements: breathing lines, closed-eye figure, stars\\nScene/backdrop: must include soft lifestyle elements throughout: pillows, moon, stars, hot milk, aromatherapy, books, eye masks, curtains, beds\\nLighting/mood: needs a gentle, soothing, sleep-healing atmosphere — exact light source mix is yours\\nColor palette: must be cream white, light beige, pale oatmeal, light caramel dominant, with small amounts of dark brown text — exact hex values are yours\\nMaterials/textures: needs a soft, tactile, premium editorial feel — exact material choices are yours\\nText (verbatim): must include all Chinese text as specified in Subject field above, large and readable, no English\\nConstraints: must be 3:4 vertical format suitable for Xiaohongshu, 9-grid must be cleanly divisible, all text in Chinese only, no text near grid boundaries, magazine-quality layout, premium aesthetic suitable for knowledge-sharing content\\nAvoid: must avoid cheap marketing vibes, overly flashy decorations, cluttered layouts, text garbling, English text\", \"size\": \"1152x1536\", \"quality\": \"medium\", \"n\": 1, \"output_format\": \"png\"}",
